News.Title: Sungarner Energies Secures 13.5 MW Solar Plant Contract in Rajasthan
News.Summary: Sungarner Energies has been awarded a contract to develop a 13.5 MW solar power plant in Rajasthan. The contract is valued at approximately 320 million rupees (including GST), demonstrating the company's continued growth in the renewable energy sector.
